Cliffjumper now holstered his gun. These Maximals think like I do. "I
also disagree with Iron Raptor's leadership. I'm Cliffjumper," He said,
now more friendly. 

Beachcomber pulled around the corner, finally chatching up to
Cliffjumper. He transformed, and was a bit suprised to see him with
other Maximals.
